died by this manifestation of sup\nport, but trading interest lagged.\nInvestment confidence in the car\nrier issues, shaken by the severe New\nYear decline, improved as the list took\nup a second week of buoyant recovery.\nThis appeared in the place of the\nearlier \"fear psychology,\u201d engendered\nby the Erie's move for reorganization,\nwhich dominated the market through\nthe long decline. Also contributing to\nthe more hopeful sentiment on the\nrailroad outlook was a widely expressed\nopinion the roads would be given at\nleast a part of the requested 15 per\ncent freight rate increase. The I. C.\nC. decision on this was expected before\nMarch 1.\nThe two weeks\u2019 rebound brought\ngains ranging from 4 to around 12\npoints in a large number of repre\nsent ative carrier issues, including those\nof Baltimore Ohio. Cleveland Union\nTerminal, Erie, Great Northern, Illi\nnois Central, New York Central.\nNorthern Pacific. Southern Pacific and\nPennsylvania. In some inactive rails\nthe recoveries from the January lows\nran from 15 to 18 points.\nThere was a modest revival of trad\ning interest in certain indusirial con\nvertibles as related shares moved up\nhill. Utilities also tended to improve\nin the late sessions.\nDespite its breadth, trading con\ntinued in low figures. This suggested\na continued absence from the market\nof dealers concerned over the uncer\ntain business outlook and political\nfactors.\nUnited States Governments moved\nsluggishly in a narrow trading range.\nINSURANCE\nDo you have insurance on sour\nfurnishings? We can secure proper\ncoverage at reasonable rates. Write\nor call\nFEDER \\I.-AMERICAN COMPANY\nK\u00ab; 15th St. N.W*. NA. 303*1\nThe\nPERSONAL ATTENTION\nriven\nvour property by our active man\nagement department insures smart,\neconomical operation.\nCONSI'LT IS TODAY.\nNo obligation for our opinion.\nFEDERAL-AMERICAN COMPANY\nHOT I rah St. N.W.NA. HOT?\nSafe Investments\n60. First Mortgage Note*\nyQ Secured on conserva\ntively appr